{"tid":1846520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽 唔好自亂陣腳啊！！！","createTime":"2020-01-27T15:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:45:46.000Z","uid":236080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"428c74455ce942c5ab89f15ffb49d1e8018bd960","tid":1846520,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"宜家人心惶惶，每個香港人都好驚自己會中招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咳 / 呼吸怪怪地 / 流鼻水 / 喉嚨痛 /  喉嚨痕 / 冇精神 /....</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實凍天有以上病症好<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>正常</strong></span>，唔一定係武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n只要戴好口罩，做好個人衛生，做好保暖，無論有冇唔舒服都戴好口罩保護自己，唔會有事㗎！<br />\n<br />\n我一聽到話有肺炎就成日覺得自己好似透唔到氣，呼吸唔到，仲有時成日覺得自己想咳。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，試下盡可能放鬆自己，慢慢調節呼吸，訓一訓教會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n只要你仲有食慾，就多數唔會係感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n萬一真係有齊以上症狀或者好驚，戴好口罩保護自己同其他人，盡快求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">好多時都係心理作用影響生理</span><br />\n香港人，放鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假日唔敢去人多地方，可以去郊區行下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYadHey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYadHey.jpg&h=98852c46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cc667a6b2146baf115da16f90865fdb94419625","tid":1846520,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"只要做好自己嘅個人衛生<br />\n唔洗驚會中招！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放鬆啲"},{"pid":"4f63d9c5c51dd672dc6fb074ee87f165f3416bac","tid":1846520,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"心理影響生理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e1fc5ab99d91acaaacd6011d5d1987dd9254ef","tid":1846520,"uid":301139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c