es/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己做好保護<br />\n係咁咳"},{"pid":"dc569cc897cb9ad4cf1a8aa9946288439d40aa01","tid":1846520,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[合法罷工 ， 助己助人]<br />\n本身你在醫院/海關/巴士司機/ 金融/任何政府崗位工作<br />\n又有傷風感冒症狀 （很容易自製冷親)<br />\n請上齊裝備即刻去急症室睇醫生 醫生一定畀你嚇親畀假紙你 甚至將你隔離 變相罷工， 即時救港行動<br />\n只要你有輕微發燒症狀， 拍片做證 ，你老細就吹你唔脹， 你問:係唔係要返工傳染畀同事先至安樂？<br />\n病假救港、助己助人、刻不容緩</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed70109beae4a74be1a275339a3440d71351698a","tid":1846520,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 其實同而家高病發既流感好似<br />\n<br />\n所以真係唔洗太嚇自己住  <br />\n<br />\n但有病一定要帶口罩！！！"},{"pid":"6428319dae8793d3b73fd9b7fe5f6e8dba6c381f","tid":1846520,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76837a27fbf96598753703fb66d1aab8370b979","tid":1846520,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed70109beae4a74be1a275339a3440d71351698a","tid":1846520,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 其實同而家高病發既流感好似<br />\n<br />\n所以真係唔洗太嚇自己住  <br />\n<br />\n但有病一定要帶口罩！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"做好個人衛生<br />\n隔離支爆都唔影響"},{"pid":"35c383c404f32a01a9c7bfb7dcc5ca113a93fbb2","tid":1846520,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09983da4f8aca2d99c23ce73dc5d38978771b42","tid":1846520,"uid":301139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ff06e17b05a6870db450e965891ff362093bb1","tid":18